imdb.plot outline: Join Pastor J and Friends as they have riveting discussions about religion, life, and spirituality within the LGBTQ community. The show that finally discusses religion from the LGBTQ viewpoint. The discussions, the drama, the advice, the taboo subject all in one show. Its all love on the Empowerment Zone w/Pastor J and Friends.
